# ── Secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Never commit. Whitelist a public key with `!path/to/pubkey.asc` if ever needed.
.env*
!.env.example
!.env.template
!.env.sample
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*.jks
id_rsa
id_rsa.pub
id_ed25519
id_ed25519.pub
id_ecdsa
id_ecdsa.pub
*-private*.asc
*-private*.gpg
*-private*.key
secrets/
.secrets/

